{
"#name"
:
{
"git"
:
{
"cn"
:
"为 git 设计的增强模块"
,
"en"
:
"Enhanced modules for git"
}
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x git [subcmd] [options]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x git status"
:
null
}
,
{
"x git add <file>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x git commit -m message"
:
null
}
]
,
"#meta"
:
{
"default-subcmd"
:
"status"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Git 分布式版本控制系统的增强模块。\n提供分支管理、配置管理、局部仓库管理、同步操作等增强功能，\n以及与 GitHub/GitLab 等平台的集成功能。\n\n**特色功能:**\n- 快捷克隆：支持 :gh/:gt/:gl 等短名和自动补全 owner\n- 分支增强：快速创建、复制、删除分支\n- 局部仓库：稀疏检出(sparse-checkout)管理大仓库\n- 批量操作：跨多个仓库执行 push/pull/track\n- 服务提供商：针对中国网络优化的代理配置\n"
,
"en"
:
"Enhanced module for Git distributed version control system.\nProvides enhanced features for branch management, configuration management,\npartial repository management, sync operations, and integration with GitHub/GitLab platforms.\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Quick clone: Support :gh/:gt/:gl shortcuts and auto-complete owner\n- Branch enhancement: Quickly create, copy, delete branches\n- Partial repo: Sparse-checkout management for large repositories\n- Batch operations: Execute push/pull/track across multiple repositories\n- Service providers: Proxy configuration optimized for China network\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"**克隆快捷方式:**\n- `x git clone :gh/user/repo` → 克隆 GitHub 仓库\n- `x git clone :gt/user/repo` → 克隆 Gitee 仓库\n- `x git clone repo` → 自动使用默认 owner 克隆\n\n**cl vs clone:**\n- `cl`: 轻量克隆，跳过 LFS 大文件下载，适合快速浏览\n- `clone`: 完整克隆，支持所有选项，克隆后自动应用 gitconfig\n\n**常用快捷命令:**\n- `x git a` = `git add .`\n- `x git ac \"msg\"` = `git add . && git commit -m`\n- `x git ss` = `git status -s`\n- `x git ci` = 增强的 commit 命令\n- `x git pp` = `git pull && git push`\n"
,
"en"
:
"**Clone shortcuts:**\n- `x git clone :gh/user/repo` → Clone GitHub repository\n- `x git clone :gt/user/repo` → Clone Gitee repository\n- `x git clone repo` → Clone with default owner\n\n**cl vs clone:**\n- `cl`: Lightweight clone, skip LFS large files, good for quick browsing\n- `clone`: Full clone with all options, auto-apply gitconfig after clone\n\n**Common shortcuts:**\n- `x git a` = `git add .`\n- `x git ac \"msg\"` = `git add . && git commit -m`\n- `x git ss` = `git status -s`\n- `x git ci` = Enhanced commit command\n- `x git pp` = `git pull && git push`\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x git clone :gh/x-cmd/x-cmd"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 克隆 GitHub 仓库（使用 :gh 短名）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Clone GitHub repository (using :gh shortcut)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git clone :gt/x-cmd/x-cmd"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 克隆 Gitee 仓库（使用 :gt 短名）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Clone Gitee repository (using :gt shortcut)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git cl :gh/x-cmd/x-cmd"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 轻量克隆，跳过 LFS 大文件"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Lightweight clone, skip LFS large files"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git status"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看工作树状态"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show working tree status"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git a && x git ac 'fix: bug'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 添加所有文件并提交"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Add all files and commit"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git branch ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有分支"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all branches"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git part clone :gh/x-cmd/x-cmd"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 稀疏克隆，只下载顶层目录"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Sparse clone, only download top-level directory"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x git sp setup localhost:9999"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 设置代理优化国内访问"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Setup proxy for China network optimization"
}
]
