"cl"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Lightweight clone, skip LFS large files (GIT_LFS_SKIP_SMUDGE=1)"
,
"cn"
:
"轻量克隆，跳过 LFS 大文件下载"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"`cl` 是 `clone` 的轻量版本，设置 GIT_LFS_SKIP_SMUDGE=1 跳过 LFS 文件下载。\n适合快速浏览仓库代码，不需要大文件的情况。\n需要完整克隆（包括 LFS 文件）请使用 `clone`。\n"
,
"en"
:
"`cl` is a lightweight version of `clone`, sets GIT_LFS_SKIP_SMUDGE=1 to skip LFS files.\nGood for quickly browsing repository code without large files.\nUse `clone` for full clone (including LFS files).\n"
}
]
,
