"clone"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Full clone with all options, auto-apply gitconfig after clone"
,
"cn"
:
"完整克隆，支持所有选项，克隆后自动应用 gitconfig"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"`clone` 是完整功能的克隆命令，支持所有 git clone 选项。\n克隆后会自动进入目录并应用 `x git config apply`。\n支持多种快捷 URL 格式：\n- `:gh/user/repo` → git@github.com:user/repo\n- `:gt/user/repo` → git@gitee.com:user/repo\n- `:gl/user/repo` → git@gitlab.com:user/repo\n- `repo` → 使用默认 owner 自动补全\n"
,
"en"
:
"`clone` is full-featured clone command, supports all git clone options.\nAuto-enters directory and applies `x git config apply` after clone.\nSupports various URL shortcuts:\n- `:gh/user/repo` → git@github.com:user/repo\n- `:gt/user/repo` → git@gitee.com:user/repo\n- `:gl/user/repo` → git@gitlab.com:user/repo\n- `repo` → auto-completes with default owner\n"
}
]
